  <span class="hero__badge">Module 03</span>
  <h1 class="hero__title">Cookie Stealing</h1>
  <p class="hero__subtitle">Understanding cookies, how they're stolen, real-world case studies, XSS-based POC exploits, and complete remediation strategies.</p>
