    <div class="code-block">
      <div class="code-block__header">
        <span class="code-block__lang">Bash — Attack Flow</span>
        <button class="code-block__copy">Copy</button>
      </div>
      <pre><code># Step 1: Victim visits the vulnerable app and gets a session cookie
GET /login → Set-Cookie: session_token=user_secret_session_abc123

